      "description": "Affordable and straightforward, this vehicle offers an accessible entry point for anyone seeking basic transportation, a starter project, or a practical work-use car. It shows its age and is best suited for a buyer who values function and price over cosmetics, but it presents a solid opportunity at an approachable price point. A sensible choice for someone who wants dependable utility without a big investment.",
