      "description": "Looking for an affordable car with plenty of life left in it? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a straightforward, budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable basic transport or a handy little project. It\u2019s priced to make sense, and if you\u2019re after honest value rather than showroom shine, this could be a great fit. Come have a look, take it for a spin, and see if it suits what you need.",
