    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Tough, no-nonsense used car with strong project-driver appeal. Advertised in poor condition, but it still offers a solid platform for someone who wants affordable transportation, a starter build, or a mechanical refresher project. The powertrain feels like a usable foundation, and the chassis has the kind of straightforward, serviceable character that makes it attractive to hands-on owners. Expect cosmetic wear, age-related imperfections, and the usual needs that come with an inexpensive vehicle, but for the right buyer this is a practical way into ownership without spending big. Priced to move for someone who sees value in a fix-it-and-drive-it opportunity.",
      "price": 6900.0,
